      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just hard to accept. everyone talks about \"finding meaning\" or \"fighting through the dark,\" but that feels like a lie. if the universe really is just this cold, empty void, then all that struggle is just... unnecessary. why should anyone have to keep performing this charade of living if there's nothing waiting for us?",
